metadata.title: Shaboozey, BigXthaPlug - Drink Don't Need No Mix (Official Video)
metadata.creator: Shaboozey

tracks.text: Text appears. Drink Don't Need No Mix. Shaboozey, BigXthaPlug. A Paperwork Studio film. Directed by JMP. Young women in tight clothes approach a bar named Lucky's.
A young white man with short hair falls to the ground, eyes closed.
At the bar, Shaboozey gestures for another drink.
People smile, holding glasses and a pool cue.
The young man bends over outside. Shaboozey takes a glass with 2 fingers of brown liquid.
Seen from above, people mingle in close quarters
The young man takes a tallboy from someone. Shaboozey stands at a pool table.
Shaboozey shows a bottle of Jack Daniels. BigXthaPlug drinks from a Don Julio 1942 bottle.
Girls shake curvy butts in tight jeans and short shorts.
A man pours Jack Daniels from the bottle into a woman's open mouth.
Shaboozey dances in the parking lot.
A man readies pool balls, and Shaboozey readies his cue
A scantily clad woman lies on a pool table. People spill drinks on her, and a man presses his forehead onto her stomach.
A young man shotguns a Miller Light. An old man points at his glass.
A man lies back as alcohol is poured into his mouth
People clink glasses of different sizes and colors. Others squint and smile
BigXthaPlug does a shot
A couple kiss, look at us, then close the door to the bathroom
A woman opens her top, then closes it again
People move around in tight corners. Our view is like a spotlight. We can only see in front of us, and everything else is dark.
Shaboozey, a tall black man in a denim jacket, drinks from a plastic cup. Nearby, women drink and smile. A woman with a bird tattoo on her arm dances.
The young man wanders through the crowd. Someone hands him a cup and he drinks
He stumbles into the bathroom and hangs his head over the toilet.
Shaboozey holds out a hand to a woman sitting on a car. She takes it and hops down.
The young man, bleary eyed looking into a white spotlight, rises slowly. He rubs his head and looks around. Credits roll.
